      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That doesn't make much sense. An \"efficient algorithm\" doesn't just make the actual *available* capacity disappear. If anything, optimization should show us more headroom for our workloads. The logs show a consistent 20% deficit in raw compute availability compared to our contract. Can you explain why that specific amount is missing?",
